Uses of Dialect in org.openbel.framework.api
 

Classes in org.openbel.framework.api that implement Dialect
 class DefaultDialect
          Simple dialect that uses the BEL short form of the first supporting term found for a Kam.KamNode.
This implementation caches labels for nodes and is thus suitable only for a single Kam.
